msgid "The **Tool-Tip** options for digiKam are set from :menuselection:`Settings --> Configure digiKam... --> Tool-Tip page`. Options on this page control what information is displayed when the mouse hovers over a file icon in the Image Area. Each checkbox enables or disables the display of the specified information. The tool tip font and size can be selected from the top option on the right."
msgstr ""

